Text: Re FW You still suck at baseballon hooking up with a little longterm action Always thought youd be one of the first to go Send her down south to Portland if it looks like shes getting board with your itsy bitsy Ive kept in touch with Carl and Brett but not much else Funny how time can just slip by I think back to the days in school and yupjust like I thought everything seems so cool I think of how nice it would be to have scores of friends within a block and three bars to choose from but it didnt seem that super at the time I specifically remember getting pissed on a Tuesday night playing darts at Shakers with throngs of something girls around and shrugging it off as boring You may be suprised to hear it but I am still on with Enron and looking forward to a buyout in a week or so As strange as it may seem this whole fiscad may have been a huge blessing in disguiseIll just keep my fingers crossed Im doing a lot of skiing this year Let me know when and where we should meet up Id like to see the likes of Toby Ty Nate Ken and even Palmy got fuel to burn got roads to ride Neil Young Deano Original Message From Dean Craig Craig NRONcom Date Mon Dec To Subject FW You still suck at baseball Original Message From Oliver Smith mailto Sent Monday December PM To Dean Craig Subject You still suck at baseball CRAIG What the hell have you been up to I just got your email address from Carl I havent talked to him in about years either Last year I tried everything to get your address so you could come to my wedding I got married last July My wife Jennifer is just finishing up at the U so she is a little younger than us but shes really cute intelligent blah blah Anyway are you still in Portland I heard you were working at Enron but apparantly they do not know that since I tried calling several times and they had no idea who the fuck I was talking about Man Enron has had a tough time Amazing considering the talent that works at that companynot being sarcastic You should do the prudent thing and become a teacherbaseball coach like meno stress summers off and job security Plus the pay is not as bad as its made out to beconsidering you get a pension when you retire I love it Anyway I dont feel like typing anymore so either give me a call or I can give you a call if you send your number Id love to catch up My cell Call after yes that is the end of my work day Hope
